g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"22d35d7c823b52791d29cda4864c8505afc9fb73","tid":410554,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8247ea858ac6e4a4279c591dd0e42ecfab11f52","tid":410554,"uid":37107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"澳洲金融時報2013年7月報導，澳大利亞、美國、英國、加拿大、紐西蘭等五國家情報機構禁用聯想電腦，因有大量實驗室測試顯示，聯想電腦硬盤設有「後門」、晶片有硬體漏洞。英、澳兩國情報機構指出，聯想電路的惡意修改，超越一般典型漏洞，可被他人在無用戶個人信息授權情況下遠端操作。聯想則發表聲明，指對禁令一事不知情。此外，基於安全擔憂，美國國務院2006年決定不在機密網絡使用1.6萬台聯想電腦<br />\n<br />\n美聯社2015年2月報導指出「安全大漏洞」，聯想產品的預載軟體為以色列開發的快魚軟體（Superfish）不僅持續彈出廣告、還有助駭客竊取用戶隱私資訊；該軟體還可自行簽發安全憑證，讓使用者「把有問題的網站誤認為安全」。"},{"pid":"6c414af63c3a1c2c558e7f3e3e6a226d4e0e7cbd","tid":410554,"uid":18684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"巴打我都係y50-70 加咗ssd &amp; ram <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fdb241ecf409dc52b8785c74d3de4bee57aa26","tid":410554,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我都係y50-70 加咗ssd &amp; ram <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下你換咗邊隻，幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af25f1df86555d0ef0d5e9ae65057e4418a823f2","tid":410554,"uid":44389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打我都係y50-70 加咗ssd &amp; ram <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下你換咗邊隻，幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n850 evo"},{"pid":"caa90740d101ab0ba984b63bd47a85cd9e4c4b81","tid":410554,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,